static void ADCBUFConfigureDataFormat ( DSSRegs *  ptrDssRegBase,
uint8_t  dataFormat,
uint8_t  interleave,
uint8_t  iqConfig 
)
static

Description
Configure ADC Buffer data format.

Parameters
[in]ptrDssRegBasePointer to the DSS Register Base
[in]dataFormat0 for complex, 1 for real data format.
[in]interleaveEnable interleave mode.
[in]iqConfigIn complex mode, 0 to store as Q(MSB) + I(LSB), 1 to store as I(MSB) +Q(LSB) In Real mode, this field is don't care
Return values
N/A

static void ADCBUFTestPatternConfig ( DSSRegs *  ptrDssRegBase,
const ADCBuf_TestPatternConf *  testPatternConf 
)
static

Description
Configure Test pattern for ADC Buffer. Based on the passed values, it sets up the offset and value for each successive sample for the test pattern IQ data, for each of the 4 channels. It also configures period between successive samples of test pattern, and number of samples to store(per channel) in each Ping and Pong register in continuous mode of ADC Buffer.

Parameters
[in]ptrDssRegBasePointer to the DSS Register Base
[in]testPatternConfConfiguratio of test pattern for all channels
Return values
N/A
